lyrics:
[verse]
In this hazy room, thoughts start to collide
Lost in a daze, I cannot hide
Your smile pulls me closer, like a magnetic force
Love's gentle embrace, forever on its course

[chorus]
Losing my mind, caught in your gaze
In this lofi rhythm, love sets ablaze
Melodies of affection, soft and serene
With you by my side, love's sweetest dream
